reviewText: Total theory and theory, no practical work, just theory and all the information is available for free on Google and YouTube.
The Digital Marketing Institute program is a diploma mill. The passing assignment is 100% peer reviewed (graded by other students).
Absolutely educative, engaging and empowerng course and course delivery.

The course flows lucidly by evaluating on digital strategy execution and management, core areas of CX and development, digital risks and data protection along with inculcating leadership values and mindset at various levels.It gives a proper understanding of how to create and facilitate a team in your organization.Although some measures of improvement can be there!Overall, it is a wholesome course which completes the entire specialization by catapulting its value.
A very engaging course, I learnt a lot and feel good about the time i invested into the course
It is insightful. It is worth it when we look for Digital strategy or digital marketing mindset

I​t's pretty concise about all the topics including a management role in Marketing, and how one can become a leader by helping others. 

Thank you for the oppertunity.
Very good course. Learned alot. It is a good course for the beginners. I recommend this course for all who want to learn digital marketing.
O​ne of the best courses that I have enjoyed studying. the knowledge that is in these 3 weeks, is unbelievable. Thank you DMI
excellent content i really enjoyed this course and learn digital strategy and planning excecution .
Everything was explained quite well. I do have an issue with how long it can take for the Peer Reviews to be completed, but that can't really be helped much.
